Garwe (crocodile in English) imhuka inogara mumvura inowanikwa munzvimbo inodziya ye "tropics" mumatunhu ari kuAfrica, Asia neAustralia. Makarwe anogara mumvura isina munyu munzizi, nyanza, madziva nematoro.

Makarwe anodya nyama inosanganisira [[hove]]; mhuka dzemumvura nemhuka dzepadunhu. Mune dzimwe nyika makarwe anopfuyiwa pama[[purazi]], matehwe acho achizoshandiswa kugadzira [[shangu]] nemabheki emadzimai. Nyama yemuskwe wegarwe inokosheswa se[[mutakunanzva]] kunzvimbo dzinoshanyirwa dzakaita se Victoria Falls. Nyama iyi inotaridzika senyama ye[[huku]].
